message: "If you use this repository, please cite the software and the associated dataset."
title: "CodeJudgeEval-X: Diagnosing LLM Misjudgments in Automated Code Evaluation"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "CodeJudgeEval-X Team"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: 2026-03-17
abstract: >-
  Codebase for constructing CodeJudge-Eval-X evaluation files. It augments
  the CodeJudge-Eval dataset with static code quality metrics and
  problem-level metrics, and includes code for the logistic and RF
  classifiers used in the study.
